You guys are always asking me how I like my PXG’s…
I know there are plenty of golfers out there who have yet to even try a @pxg GEN6 driver…
Well my friends, now is the *perfect* time to “put your money where your mouth is.” 😏
•Bring in your existing driver to a local PXG store.
•Once warmed up, take five shots with your current driver (keeping the best three) and do the same with the recommended GEN6 driver
•If PXG doesn’t beat your current driver on distance or dispersion, YOU get $100
 
…it’s that simple.
